1. json
apt-get install libjsoncpp-dev
头文件在：
/usr/include/jsoncpp/json
动态库在：
/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libjsoncpp.so.1.7.2



2. libevent
官方地址http://libevent.org/
./configure –prefix=/usr
make
make install



3.openssl
 apt-get install openssl
 apt-get install libssl-dev



4.Cryptopp
 apt-get install libcrypto++*



5. libcurl
apt-get install libcurl4-openssl-dev
头文件：/usr/include/curl
库文件：/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libcurl.so.4



6.libuuid
apt-get install uuid-dev



7.Libevhtp
github下载:https://github.com/criticalstack/libevhtp
cd build
cmake ..
make
make install

或：apt-get instal libevhtp-dev


8. mysqlclient-dev
  apt-get install libmysqlclient-dev
